Detailed Description

template<class KeyType, class DataType>
class SetMap< KeyType, DataType >

This class is a STL map of sets.

Use it when you want something sorted sorted by something else. Main benefit is that you don't have to create the elements in the map.

KeyType The type used as key in the map. DataType The type used for the elements of the set.
